reviews.review_text: June 3, 1995 My second to last Grateful Dead concert.  I had a great time, all 3 days.  My friend, Danny Lucian was one of the tapers apparently.  Would love to get in touch with him, it has been about 30 years since I saw him.  Thanks to Matthew Vernon for your tireless efforts in uploads to the archive.  Forrest S. George
